Are you having trouble controlling the way you eat? 
&#8232;

Free Food Addicts in Recovery Anonymous (FA)Twelve Step meetings.  The FA recovery program is for anyone suffering from food obsession, overeating, under-eating, bulimia or other food-related issues. Weekly meetings every Wednesday evening 7 - 8:30 pm at the Brighthelm Center - Pelham room, North Road, Brighton, East Sussex BN1 1YD.  Free parking available in car park; 5-minute walk from Brighton Station and central Bus route.  All are welcome.
